{"tid":653200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"汪洋：我學廣東話誰敢廢","createTime":"2018-05-04T13:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T10:04:34.000Z","uid":144372,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0db6dd8b9b0b36d95d81c29a53cc484a96c4c507","tid":653200,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20100805/656139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20100805%2F656139&d=znF%2FQio4JK0JxDHoy3xseEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1a0f5647\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20100805/656139</a><br />\n<br />\n針對日前粵語存廢問題引發極大爭議，廣東省委書記汪洋公開回應，「我都在學廣東話，誰敢廢粵？」更痛批「推普廢粵」是偽命題，根本是子虛烏有的事。<br />\n汪洋4日出席即將登場的亞運會倒數100天誓師大會上，表示近來流傳「推普去粵語化」是無中生有。事實上，自從他到廣東上任後，經常帶頭學粵語，也囑咐到當地工作的官員也要學習該語言。<br />\n汪洋也說，包括一些恐怖份子在內的有心人士，最近利用這個議題不斷操作集會來做其他的事。他更舉例在1日集會被逮捕的3人裡，有2名就有案底，另外還有3成或4成是學生，所以大家要提高警惕，千不萬要被利用，因為「天下不是太平的」。 <br />\n根據陸媒報導指出，粵語一直是廣東人的母語，也一直受到大陸尊重，在中國改革開放初期，還不少廣東歌被傳唱至今。反觀廣東人學普通話，是因應現在生活與經濟需求，對於不同語言和方言都應該被保護。"},{"pid":"2580fd4618ef76dc5efbed0d4664bdc8ba0ec9e2","tid":653200,"uid":57835,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"咁香港教育而家變成點先，你鐘意用廣東話關我地撚事咩"},{"pid":"12027762ae66bfe11e188d4b5b4c7f1b70ad1902","tid":653200,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"一朝天子一朝臣"},{"pid":"72c30d2639982541e7a80286c9665b4aa5d4c69c","tid":653200,"uid":18724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:46:49.000Z","msg":"近呢十年，土共一邊要求廣東省電視台用廣東話播出要先申請，增加電視台用粵語廣播既繁複程序，對想使用粵語既電視台造成麻煩，一邊又話自己推廣緊粵語誰敢廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecd08441a8c07e3f98a3bdc320b9b62de060aa5","tid":653200,"uid":45353,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"呢條友不嬲扮開明或白面<br />\n<br />\n仲八面玲瓏<br />\n<br />\n擺撚明團派咁都無事仲受重用"},{"pid":"9fab74e283240813d7046e3fcf998a8537fbf21a","tid":653200,"uid":57513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"8年前既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4fe96aaf2c3464aaab754572a14d302f345d59","tid":653200,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fab74e283240813d7046e3fcf998a8537fbf21a","tid":653200,"uid":57513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"8年前既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"屌原來係咁"},{"pid":"d72fdf266bae5e8dd3f0246d727a0ffd7f15e47b","tid":653200,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4fe96aaf2c3464aaab754572a14d302f345d59","tid":653200,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fab74e283240813d7046e3fcf998a8537fbf21a","tid":653200,"uid":57513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"8年前既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"屌原來係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"證明8年前已經打壓緊囉"},{"pid":"5ad0f11f34094b68d074a014eee469020e1e8bc5","tid":653200,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"共產黨人講嘅嘢都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba611f4cb12836a4624e48fca88744b6ca6cfee","tid":653200,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"講出黎唔係比我地聽既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講一回事做就另一回事喇"}]}